<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau thiengtho meikuong leh meipi a mapui,
 Lal Immanuel hung nai kitin;
 Sietlei lampi thima ka vaih lai hin,
 Hung vak kitin, pielgal Zingsawl,
 Aksi vak hawih tak chu.

[V2]
 Aw van Aksi, aw van Aksi vak hawih,
 Ka Hukdampa leh ka lal deihum pen Na hi;
 Lungkhamna kinawk in dogal hunglien mahleh,
 Bitna Lalpa bel ing ie kumsawt in.

[V3]
 2. Suongmantam dawngkawt hawih lopi hawn a hih tieng,
 Sana tuol nuom achun leng tangka;
 Gitloh zieka ka lungkhamna cheng hi,
 Gam lopi ninnawpna munah;
 Pakthing banglun tan a.

[V4]
 3. Belam No lalna gam nitum ngeilo achun,
 Khensa te'n nuoi simlei ngai loin;
 Zaila'n Belam No chu a chawian ui,
 Hinna thing bak lim nuoiah;
 Puon thieng silh in a leng ui.

[V5]
 4. Ka lenna ding chung thangvan gam ninnuom a chun,
 Sietlei hinkhuo sang muol a liem tieng;
 Khensa guol ngaih laia va bang buolin,
 Ninnawp kiemlo in Lal nunnem;
 Chawian in la sang ka.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Van Aksi</title>
<hymn_number>106</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Zasiama</author>
</song>